#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:2
msgid "Share / Access"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:4
msgid ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-share-alt\"></i> Share and <i class=\"fa fa-unlock-"
"alt\"></i> Access are the two menus to manage how other users can "
"interact with your documents on CryptPad."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:6
msgid ""
"From the document toolbar: <i class=\"fa fa-share-alt\"></i> Share and <i"
" class=\"fa fa-unlock-alt\"></i> Access at the center."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:7
msgid ""
"From the CryptDrive: Right click on a document > <i class=\"fa fa-share-"
"alt\"></i> Share or <i class=\"fa fa-unlock-alt\"></i> Access."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:10
msgid "Share"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:12
msgid ""
"There are three ways to share a document: [Contacts], [Link], and "
"[Embed]. In each case, access rights can be set to authorise the "
"recipient to edit the document, or to only view it."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:14
msgid "Access rights"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:16
msgid "There are 4 levels of permissions:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:18
msgid "View: Read-only without editing the document."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:19
msgid ""
"Present: Read-only the rendered output of the document, available in the "
"[Code] and [Slides] applications."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:20
msgid "Edit: View and make changes to the document."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:21
msgid ""
"View once and self-destruct: Read-only one time. Once the link is opened "
"by a recipient, the document is deleted permanently."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:23
msgid ""
"Note: If a document is already stored in the CryptDrive of a user with "
"edit rights, the \"edit link\" is shown in the document's properties even"
" if the user is in View mode."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:25
msgid "Sharing with contacts"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:26
#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:77
#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:112
msgid "{logged in user}"
msgstr "{**utilisateur connecté**}"

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:28
msgid ""
"This is the recommended method for sharing documents securely on "
"CryptPad. When sharing directly with [contacts], document links never "
"leave the encrypted platform of CryptPad. This prevents data from being "
"leaked to third parties."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:30
msgid "To share with one or more contacts:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:32
msgid ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-share-alt\"></i> Share in the document toolbar > <i "
"class=\"fa fa-address-book\"></i> Contacts."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:33
msgid ""
"Right click on the document in the CryptDrive > <i class=\"fa fa-share-"
"alt\"></i> Share > <i class=\"fa fa-address-book\"></i> Contacts."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:35
msgid "Then:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:37
#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:72
msgid "Choose the [access rights]."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:38
msgid "Select the contacts or teams to share with."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:39
msgid "Share button."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:41
msgid ""
"When sharing with contacts, they receive a notification.<br />When "
"sharing with a team, the document is added directly to the team's "
"CryptDrive."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:44
msgid "Sharing a link"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:46
msgid ""
"The Link tab provides links that can be shared through the medium of your"
" choice. Depending on how you send the link, this method can present "
"security risks. To add a level of security, it is recommended to add a "
"[password] to your document before sharing the link."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:48
msgid "To copy the link to a document:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:50
msgid ""
"From the document: <i class=\"fa fa-share-alt\"></i> Share in the toolbar"
"  > <i class=\"fa fa-link\"></i> Link"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:51
msgid ""
"From the CryptDrive : Right click on the document > <i class=\"fa fa-"
"share-alt\"></i> Share > <i class=\"fa fa-link\"></i> Link"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:53
#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:70
msgid "then"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:55
msgid ""
"Choose the [access rights].<br />Embed mode hides the toolbar and user "
"list<br />Preview allows to check what the link will look like before "
"sending it."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:58
msgid "Copy the link."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:59
msgid "Send the link."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:61
msgid "Embedding"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:63
msgid "Embedding allows for a CryptPad document to be displayed on a web page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:65
msgid "To embed a document:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:67
msgid ""
"From the document : <i class=\"fa fa-share-alt\"></i> Share in the "
"toolbar > <i class=\"fa fa-code\"></i> Embed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:68
msgid ""
"From the CryptDrive : Right click on the document > <i class=\"fa fa-"
"share-alt\"></i> Share > <i class=\"fa fa-code\"></i> Embed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:73
msgid "Copy the embed code."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:74
msgid "Paste the code on a web page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:76
msgid "Shared folders"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:79
msgid "Shared folders are made for sharing a set of documents at once."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:81
msgid "To create a shared folder in the CryptDrive:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:83
msgid "+ New > <i class=\"cptools cptools-shared-folder\"></i> Shared folder."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:84
msgid "Ctrl + e > <i class=\"cptools cptools-shared-folder\"></i> Shared folder."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:85
msgid ""
"Right click > <i class=\"cptools cptools-shared-folder\"></i> New shared "
"folder."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:87
msgid "To convert an existing folder into a shared folder:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:89
#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:101
msgid "Right click on the folder > <i class=\"fa fa-share-alt\"></i> Share."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:90
msgid "Choose the conversion options.<br />Password.<br />[Owned] folder."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:93
msgid "OK or press the Enter key."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:99
msgid ""
"Folders are shared in a similar way to documents. To share a folder from "
"the CryptDrive:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:102
msgid ""
"Choose the [access rights].<br />View: Read-only without editing the "
"contents of the folder.<br />Edit: View and make changes to the folder."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:105
msgid ""
"Three tabs are available:<br /><i class=\"fa fa-address-book\"></i> "
"Contacts: Recommended method to share securely with contacts and teams on"
" CryptPad.<br /><i class=\"fa fa-link\"></i> Link: Copy a link to send "
"through the medium of your choice.<br /><i class=\"fa fa-code\"></i> "
"Embed: Copy code to include the folder on a web page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:111
msgid "Access"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:114
msgid "This menu is used to restrict access to a document or shared folder:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:116
msgid "From the document: <i class=\"fa fa-unlock-alt\"></i> Access."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:117
msgid ""
"From the CryptDrive: Right click on the document or shared folder > <i "
"class=\"fa fa-unlock-alt\"></i> Access."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:120
msgid "Access tab"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:122
msgid "This tab summarises all the modalities of access to the document:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:124
msgid ""
"Expiration date: Date at which the document will be deleted. This date is"
" set at the creation of the document and cannot be modified afterwards."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:126
msgid ""
"Password: Displays if a [password] has been set. A new password can be "
"set, or an existing password modified."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:128
msgid "Owners: List of all the document's [owners]."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:130
msgid ""
"Edit rights requests:<br />Request edit rights: For users with read-only "
"access rights.<br /><i class=\"fa fa-bell-slash\"></i> Mute access "
"requests for this pad: Hides edit rights requests for this document. "
"{document owners}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:134
msgid "Access list: Displays the [access list] and indicates if it is enabled."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:136
msgid ""
"<i class=\"cptools cptools-destroy\"></i> Destroy: Delete the document "
"permanently."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:139
msgid "Access List"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:140
#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:168
msgid "{document owners}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:142
msgid ""
"The access list restricts access to a document. Once active, users who "
"are not on the list are not able to access the document, even if they "
"have it stored in their CryptDrive."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:144
msgid ""
"To enable the access list, tick Enable access list. The [owners] of the "
"document are on the list by default and cannot be removed from it."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:146
msgid "To add contacts or teams to the list:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:148
#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:172
msgid "Select them in the list of contacts on the right."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:149
#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:173
msgid "Add them to the list with the <i class=\"fa fa-arrow-left\"></i> button."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:151
msgid ""
"To remove a user or team from the list use the <i class=\"fa fa-"
"times\"></i> button next to their name."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_guide/share_and_access.md:153
msgid "Owners"
msgstr ""

